                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#iiiv(erso) #96v #97v" facs="004 051 052">Fols. iiiv(erso), 96v, 97v</locus>
                    blank
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e3">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#ivr(ecto)" facs="004">Fol. ivr(ecto)</locus>
                    several isolated words, perhaps pen trials
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a1">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#50r" facs="054">Fol. 50r</locus>
                    student copy of an excerpt of one of the chants
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <desc>
                    The second folium stub before <locus target="#61" facs="065">fol. 61</locus> has writing on it and may be a folio that has been cut or broken rather than a half sheet
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a2">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#96r" facs="100">Fol. 96r</locus>
                    scribal note “May God bless the one who caused this book to be finished in the peace of God. Amen.”
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e5">
                    <desc>
                      words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#12v #13r #53r #54r #57r" facs="017 057 058 061">folss. 12v, 13r, 53r, 54r, 57r, </locus>, etc.);
                      words of text are written in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target="#20v #55v" facs="025 060">20v, 55v, </locus>);
                      text has been removed (<locus target="#51v #52r #54r #58v #64v" facs="056 058 063 069">51v, 52r, 54r, 58v, 64v</locus>, etc.)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                  </list>
